Desired features

* improve table handling in the PDF generation
* allow font customization in the PDF generation http://xmlgraphics.apache.org/fop/1.0/fonts.html

* equation handling - find way to run latex and produce nice output.
How to invoke latex from inside
<xsl:value-of select="Runtime:exec(Runtime:getRuntime(), 'latex')"
xmlns:Runtime="java:java.lang.Runtime"/>

to get equations http://www.fauskes.net/nb/htmleqII/ in html - or texvc from mediawiki....